<p>With storm clouds gathering, Dave and I decided to forgo the planned bailout ride and really bailout by riding Flagstaff.  Good choice.</p>
<p>Today was much like a day in winter, in that there was the feeling of a front moving through, which seems to be less frequent or noteworthy in the other three season.  It was a nice prelude for things to come.</p>